|Proportion = 1:2<ref name="fotw">[http://www.crwflags.com/fotw/flags/im.html Isle of Man]; ''[[Flags of the World]]''; (c.1996 – present)</ref>
|Adoption   = December 1, 1932
|Design     = A [[triskelion]] made up of three armoured legs with golden spurs, in the centre of a red flag.
